    THE MASTISHQ SCIENCE

    Amalgamation of your 86 billion neurones, thought processes, behavior, psychomotor activity,  speech patterns, eye movement, listening capabilities, gait, vitals and many other similar receptors, actors and indicators define & drive your mental health.  All of these provide insights to build perception, quantify severity to finally diagnose and treat. 

    We are leveraging mature traditional science to build this new patented method and technologies for data driven diagnosis, prognosis of  therapies or treatments. 

    Read More

    WHY MASTISHQ

    A different approach of addressing Mental Health.

    We are building the first ever comprehensive digital platform dedicated to mental health diagnosis and triage. It will start with 5 minutes self-screening for next action steps. This can be easily executed and reports consumed by patients themselves to know whether you really need help of Psychiatrist or Neurologist. 

    The platform can be easily accessed through a commonly available smartphones. 

    Followed by specialised testing for better details and quantified reference-able reports for Specialists, Psychologist and General Practitioners.  

    Read More

    NAVIGATE THROUGH YOUR REAL-TIME STATUS AND COMPARE

    We have mature practice of examination of pathology, radiology, genomics  and the obvious vitals etc. 

    Ironically, whenever we get into mental health conditions, we are totally dependent on the perception at that very moment and best of memory of the examiner. 

    Mastishq here brings the view as quantified value to get the severity of condition and ready for reference immediately. Also you can compare with your historical reports for better prognosis.

    Read More

    PERCEPTION ENABLED

    We are working for simulating the Doctor's precision for diagnosis and testing method. A comprehensive method of perception based on facial and physical analysis for mental health conditions using artificial intelligence aka AI.

    We want to augment medical health professionals with meaningful & reliable insights of individuals. The mundane task execution may get handled by the Mastishq platform components. This will lead to better focused medication approach and prognosis.
